                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-7 col-xxl-8">
                    <div class="border-top border-translucent">
                        <div id="purchasersSellersTable" data-list='{"valueNames":["deals_name","deal_owner","account_name","stage","amount"],"page":10,"pagination":true}'>
