                                                    Description
                                                </th>
                                                <th class="sort white-space-nowrap align-middle ps-4" scope="col" style="width:350px;">
                                                    ETAT
                                                </th>
                                                <th class="sort align-middle ps-4 pe-5 text-uppercase text-nowrap" scope="col" data-sort="amount" style="min-width:50px;">
                                                    Date
